'''Gilson Benchimol Tavares''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈʒil.sɔn bẽ.ʃi.ˈmɔl ta.ˈva.ɾɨʃ|lang}}; born 29 December 2001), is a Cape Verdean professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Striker (association football)|striker]] for Russian club [[FC Akron Tolyatti|Akron Tolyatti]] and the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Club career==
On 22 July 2024, Benchimol signed a long-term contract with [[Russian Premier League]] club [[FC Akron Tolyatti|Akron Tolyatti]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Akron Tolyatti|url=https://fcakron.ru/blog/2024/07/22/akron-podpisal-forvarda-sbornoj-kabo-verde/|title="Акрон" подписал форварда сборной Кабо-Верде|trans-title=Akron signed a forward of Cape Verde national team|date=22 July 2024|access-date=23 July 2024|language=ru}}</ref>

==International career==
Benchimol debuted for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] in a 2–1 friendly loss to [[Guinea national football team|Guinea]] on 10 October 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://inforpress.cv/futebol-jovem-internacional-cabo-verdiano-gilson-tavares-continua-em-destaque-no-estoril-praia-em-portugal/|title=Futebol: Jovem internacional cabo-verdiano Gilson Tavares continua em destaque no Estoril-Praia em Portugal|date=December 19, 2020|access-date=March 13, 2021|archive-date=May 5, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505014522/https://inforpress.cv/futebol-jovem-internacional-cabo-verdiano-gilson-tavares-continua-em-destaque-no-estoril-praia-em-portugal/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He scored a hat-trick in a game against the [[Liechtenstein national football team]] on 25 March 2022.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Reardon |first=Kevin |date=2022-03-27 |title=Nations Week at Pinatar Arena starts with Cape Verde Victory |url=https://theleader.info/2022/03/27/nations-week-at-pinatar-arena-starts-with-cape-verde-victory/ |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=The Leader Newspaper |language=en-US}}</ref>
He was named in the roster for the [[2021 Africa Cup of Nations]] when the team reached the round of 16.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/cape-verde-islands/story/4555552/cape-verde-include-veteran-quartet-for-afcon|title=Cape Verde include veteran quartet for AFCON|publisher=[[ESPN]]|date=23 December 2021}}</ref>

